From: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Aug 2018 10:10:17 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 4287/5242] MLK-19110 ARM64: dts: freescale: imx8dx: increase
 CMA size

commit  37626dc6a07d005f715f996a91bff642ad28d50f from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

Increase i.MX8QXP CMA size to 960MB to meet 4K video requirement.

Signed-off-by: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Reviewed-by: Bai Ping <ping.bai@nxp.com>
(cherry picked from commit 0134cb94f8e76a35a7d74458f27d254048e070b1)
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8dx.dtsi |    4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8dx.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8dx.dtsi
index 12c67c2..c13f563 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8dx.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8dx.dtsi
@@ -112,8 +112,8 @@
 		linux,cma {
 			compatible = "shared-dma-pool";
 			reusable;
-			size = <0 0x28000000>;
-			alloc-ranges = <0 0x96000000 0 0x28000000>;
+			size = <0 0x3c000000>;
+			alloc-ranges = <0 0x96000000 0 0x3c000000>;
 			linux,cma-default;
 		};
 	};
